# Security response headers for outcomestar.app (Cloudflare Workers static assets).
# Added 2026-07-19 after the full-stack security audit: the site previously
# served no hardening headers, leaving it iframe-embeddable (clickjacking) and
# without HSTS/CSP.
#
# The CSP allowlist is built from an actual inventory of every external origin
# the site loads:
#   challenges.cloudflare.com  Turnstile (signup/login bot check)
#   cdnjs.cloudflare.com       intl-tel-input js + css
#   app.chatwoot.com           support chat SDK, iframe and websocket
#   fonts.googleapis.com       Lora / Poppins stylesheets
#   fonts.gstatic.com          font files
#   focms-api.onrender.com     the FOCMS API (all data + media blobs)
#   educationdata.urban.org    school directory lookup (portal.js)
#   *.stripe.com               checkout + billing portal redirects
#
# 'unsafe-inline' is required for script-src because the portal uses inline
# onclick handlers throughout, and for style-src because pages carry inline
# <style> blocks. The origin allowlist is still the meaningful control: it
# blocks script injection from any host not listed above.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=(self)
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://challenges.cloudflare.com https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com https://app.chatwoot.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com; font-src 'self' data: https://fonts.gstatic.com https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com; img-src 'self' data: blob: https:; media-src 'self' blob: https:; connect-src 'self' https://focms-api.onrender.com https://app.chatwoot.com wss://app.chatwoot.com https://challenges.cloudflare.com https://educationdata.urban.org; frame-src https://challenges.cloudflare.com https://app.chatwoot.com https://js.stripe.com https://checkout.stripe.com https://billing.stripe.com; form-action 'self' https://checkout.stripe.com https://billing.stripe.com; upgrade-insecure-requests
